Novartis’s Jimenez Fires Managers for Misconduct, Pharmalot Says

-- B y   E v a   v o n   S c h a p e r
-- 
2011-05-10T11:55:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-10/novartis-s-jimenez-fires-managers-for-misconduct-pharmalot-says.html
Novartis AG (NOVN) ’s Chief Executive Officer
Joe Jimenez fired some senior managers for failing to uphold
company values,  Pharmalot  blog reported, citing an internal
company communication.  Pharmalot didn’t name the executives, nor did it specify
the number or location of the managers.  Eric Althoff , a Novartis
spokesman, wasn’t immediately available for comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eva Von Schaper in Munich Bureau at 
 evonschaper@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at 
 pserafino@bloomberg.net  